Wright [c], William John Slater - Bryan Douglas, Robert Charlton, Derek Tennyson Kevan, 
John Norman Haynes, Thomas Finney.

Notes:      Matthew Busby was officially the Scotland Manager, but Trainer Dawson Walker was 
        left in charge of the players due to the tragedy of the Munich Air Disaster in 
        February 1958, in which Busby was seriously injured.
                       


